        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><strong>Revitalizing Small and Local Businesses Act</strong></p> <p>This bill establishes a competitive grant program, administered by the Economic Development Administration, for national nonprofit organizations to partner with local organizations to provide specialized technical assistance, capacity building, and related services that support small businesses and business district revitalization in low-income, rural, and minority communities.</p>]]>
        </text>
